							</div>
			<div class="col">
				
            <div class="clearfix text-formatted field field--name-body field--type-text-with-summary field--label-hidden field__item"><p>This dataset consists of</p><ul><li>20 images of dimension 2000x1500</li><li>20 images of dimension 4000x3000</li><li>20 images of dimension 8160x6120</li></ul><p>These images contain a range of content and have been categorized into animals, food, landscape, snow, water, and night. All the images have been captured using smartphones.</p><p>All the images have a pixel depth of 8-bits per pixel per channel. Color images are represented in three-channel RGB. Grayscale images are represented in a single channel.<br>All the images are stored in .bmp format.</p></div>
      
